So, and so anyway.

00:05:59.930 --> 00:06:02.709
These, this is 90 percent fiction.

00:06:02.709 --> 00:06:08.659
So most of what's happened over the last 100 years,
and 100 years in the land of content is very old.

00:06:08.660 --> 00:06:14.920
I mean we started 10000 years ago scrawling and
scrolling in stone, and that was, that was content.

00:06:14.920 --> 00:06:18.319
Wasn't very interactive, but it had a long shelf life.

