So, so the, the thing is that you have this new market
that for some reason got into this, because of Hollywood,

00:06:26.079 --> 00:06:30.839
because of that's where the money
was, was 90 percent fiction.

00:06:30.839 --> 00:06:32.599
This is 90 percent nonfiction.

00:06:32.600 --> 00:06:37.150
When you walk into a bookstore, what
you see is 90 percent of the content is

00:06:37.149 --> 00:06:39.469
about things that people are passionate about.

00:06:39.470 --> 00:06:40.940
It's about what they're interested in.

00:06:40.939 --> 00:06:46.129
It's about business or cars or philosophy
