It is 1000 dollars.

00:14:45.370 --> 00:14:49.830
And, and the images are pristine.

00:14:49.830 --> 00:14:51.780
You know for 1000 dollars.

00:14:51.779 --> 00:14:55.959
It's totally enough to do the kind of work
that you'd want to do for your podcast.

00:14:55.960 --> 00:14:59.190
And you're going to get that, it actually shoots 1080p.

00:14:59.190 --> 00:15:03.870
And so you're able to get that full resolution
or you can bring it back down to 720p.

00:15:03.870 --> 00:15:09.570
Another thing that you want to you know think
